=Generate a personalized outreach email in HTML format for this lead:

Company Name: {{ $json["Company Name"] }}
Contact Person: {{ $json["Contact Person"] }}
Job Title: {{ $json["Job Title"] }}
Industry: {{ $json["Industry"] }}
Location: {{ $json["Location"] }}
Lead Source: {{ $json["Lead Source"] }}
Booking Status: {{ $json["Booking Status"] }}

The goal is to re-engage them and encourage a meeting booking.
Mention their company or industry naturally, and make it sound warm and specific.
Keep it clean and mobile-friendly HTML (no styles or colors).

